# Test binary fixtures for unit/integration tests

This directory contains sample binaries for testing:

- hello_world.exe - Simple Windows PE
- hello_world.elf - Simple Linux ELF
- malware_sample.exe - Test malware sample (EICAR test file)
- packed.exe - UPX packed binary
- obfuscated.exe - Obfuscated binary
- vulnerable.exe - Binary with known vulnerabilities

**Note:** These are test files only and should not be executed on production systems.
